originalText.text:
Do not use Klikn Pay! They withdrew double rent multiple times from me without notifying me (this happened to at least one other person I know). When I emailed them, they first blamed me for making a late payment (this was not true) and then tried to blame it on me for the date I marked on the Klikn pay form (the 20th, 10 days before the rent was due). However, nothing on the form says certain dates will cause issues, and the date didn't cause any issues for many months.

After 2 months of incredibly frustrating back and forth with C&W to try and get my money back, I finally contacted the Office of Faculty Housing who were alarmed at the situation and were able to help me quickly get it sorted out.
